## UI Components

### Buttons
- `btn-primary`: accent fill → hover = accent-500
- `btn-secondary`: ink fill → hover = accent fill
- `btn-ghost`: transparent, ink border → hover = ink fill

<!-- Update button colors in globals.css if accent palette changes. -->

### Language Toggle
- Shown in header and mobile menu
- Only render if site is bilingual (EN + KO)
- If EN only: remove `<LangToggle />` from Header.tsx

### Header
- Fixed, transparent on load → white/95 + border on scroll
- Brand name rendered in display font as text (not SVG)
- Mobile: hamburger → full-screen drawer

### Footer
- Dark ink background
- Three columns: brand info / sitemap / brokerage
- Ambient image strip at top (ambient-footer.jpg)
- TODO: add brokerage logo PNG if available

### Forms
- Contact form: 5-field, visible `.field-input` boxes (canvas bg + 1px border)
- Estimator: multi-fieldset, same `.field-input`
- Lead privacy line: "No newsletter, no third-party data sales."
- Success state: italic display font signoff

### Editorial components (components/editorial/)
- `DropCap` — float-left first letter on essay openers
- `PullQuote` — italic quote + attribution + hairline
- `FieldNote` — numbered card (services grid, checklist)
- `FigureWithCaption` — image + italic below-left caption
- `TableOfContents` — magazine-style numbered anchor list
- `EditorialImage` — Next/Image wrapper with framing presets (wide / square / portrait)

